title: Object don't start
text:
[Object don't start](/article/532220/object-dont-start)
Thursday, November 14, 2024 by [zg4392](/users/7398518/zg4392)) | Discussion:
[ObjectDock](/articles/objectdock)
I installed ObjectDock, and there were no errors during installation. I used it normally for 3 hours. After installing Windows system updates and restarting my computer, I found that ObjectDock could not start again. I tried the following actions, but none of them worked:
- Starting it with administrator privileges;
- Uninstalling it completely and then reinstalling it.
- Purge_ObjectDock and reinstall.
Please help me, thanks.
